data.description: Rarely available 4 bed 3.5 bath home in the quiet, well established neighborhood of Haven Manor.  This home has been well cared for, tastefully updated and is being sold by it's original owner.  The basement is finished, has brand new carpeting and a full bath.  The backyard has a brand new fence, and while it's perfect for entertaining, has been landscaped with privacy is mind.  ***All mechanicals, appliances and roof are only about 5 years old.***All carpeting is brand new.***Moments from hospital, expressways and Metra.***
